data.description: Welcome to this vintage diamond in the rough home in the hot and trendy area of Cypress Park! Located in the prime location of Montecito Heights & Cypress Park, tucked between the Arts District and Pasadena and just mins from downtown L.A. This home offers an open floor plan w/lots of natural light throughout, great space, beauty, serenity, positive energy, large bedrooms, two full baths, formal dining room, and 2 car driveway with detached garage. There are 2 parcels included with this sale (5451-004-015 & 5451-004-030) It will need some tender loving care but with a buyer's vision and imagination this can be an incredible home for a first-time buyer or savvy investors looking to upgrade or downsize. This property offers tons of potential and just perfect to create your own private, chic LA lifestyle! Close to Figueroa and the Heritage Square/Arroyo Seco Gold Line Station, FRWY 101/ 10 / 5 , Schools, Shopping, Park, Dodger Stadium, Downtown LA, Staples Center, Hollywood, Pasadena, USC medical Center, Arts District, Lincoln Park, Chinatown, and Cal State L.A.
